{"tid":733718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新關稅實施數小時 特朗普突軟化　允商界申免關稅","createTime":"2018-07-08T04:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T12:48:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"365ed2f0c7a473610e1016bc7c423c7f0bb232c8","tid":733718,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:16:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180708/20443654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F20443654&d=4I0nUGy1hPUuHKx6tC%2BvAKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=fee8759e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F20443654&h=ea8f8c5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180708/20443654</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月08日 <br />\n<br />\n新關稅實施數小時<br />\n特朗普突軟化　允商界申免關稅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180708/large/a0201a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180708%2Flarge%2Fa0201a.gif&h=0549394d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【貿易戰開打】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中美貿易戰正式開打，但不如想像中煙硝味瀰漫。美國於香港時間6日中午12時01分宣佈對價值340億美元（2,652億港元）中國商品加徵關稅，新關稅措施實施幾小時後，美國貿易代表署（USTR）公佈商品豁免關稅辦法，90天內可提申請，效期1年。對此，經濟學家關焯照向《蘋果》表示，美向中國貨加關稅前，曾徵求公眾意見，特朗普可一早提出豁免，但他選擇在開戰後才臨時宣佈，證明特朗普態度有軟化迹象。<br />\n<br />\n記者：廖智廣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據美國豁免關稅辦法顯示，在今年10月9日前，業界可申請任何獲准免於額外關稅的商品，將追溯至今年7月6日生效。為公眾提供一個申請排除特定商品機會，免被課徵額外關稅。USTR表示，審查每件申請案時，會考慮幾項要素，包括在中國之外的地方是否也供應該商品、該商品是否具戰略重要性、課徵額外關稅是否會對申請方或美國利益造成嚴重經濟損害，及是否與「中國製造2025」等產業有關。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180708/large/a0201b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180708%2Flarge%2Fa0201b.gif&h=8bc63eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料中美將尋求對話<br />\n<br />\n對華貿易戰首日，美方又公佈關稅豁免辦法，內媒質疑難道特朗普「反悔了」？對此，關焯照表示，雖未知美是因本土內部壓力或中國而作出讓步，最有可能是，宣佈關稅後，美國產業認為成本增加而出現反彈，特朗普於是提出豁免申請。另一可能性是，美國不會與中國打長期貿易戰，設豁免即不會收足第一批340億美元關稅，藉此舉緩和關係。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，中美貿易戰只有輸家，沒有贏家，開放關稅豁免申請是好事，中國求之不得，按常理美國在關稅清單暫不會加注，兩國關係會有緩和迹象，市場反應亦正面。<br />\n<br />\n世界兩大經濟體正式開戰，中國官方低調處理，民間沒有出現反美情緒，足見中方不願貿易戰加劇。中共建政以來，中美先後發生6次貿易磨擦，但幾乎都是經過磋商「和氣收場」，這次雖勝負未分，但中央社引述台灣中華經濟研究院WTO及RTA中心副執行長李淳研判，美公佈清單到7月6日生效這段期間，<br />\n美中並沒有高層次對話，尤其第一階段清單並無達到美中各自目的，而特須在年底選舉前拿出成績，北京政府也了解這事，近期應會看到美中尋求對話機會。有分析評估，8月底前會有答案。但李淳認為，中美雙方也許會透過對話對目前的關稅清單作妥協，但當美國年底選舉結束，特朗普又會考量其他政治目的而有所動作，長期來看，美中關係一定會演變為長期對抗局面。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n11年來首次　美兩艦越台海<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11年來首次　美兩艦越台海<br />\n<br />\n晤華爾街高層　中方打聽特心意不果<br />\n<br />\n林鄭引習語錄暗斥美國"},{"pid":"1b8c51cec4f295cfe0968ebfbaeb7cf0dcfb06fb","tid":733718,"uid":99827,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"贏國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4dae3cee88e12fbfc78048908af27b7b94828d7","tid":733718,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a7f415731d361963efd06ec56549735a8ad9870","tid":733718,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"蘋果作新聞<br />\n突佢老母咩<br />\n原本份野一早有講俾人申訴"},{"pid":"8df7d629a0d0bd02eea276711a706039ebb9a541","tid":733718,"uid":63154,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a7f415731d361963efd06ec56549735a8ad9870","tid":733718,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"蘋果作新聞<br />\n突佢老母咩<br />\n原本份野一早有講俾人申訴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:19:26.000Z","msg":"蘋果心繫支國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f81dcfc363f7ab9ca31974def5cbcbca11a60790","tid":733718,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:22:58.000Z","msg":"USTR recognizes that some U.S. companies may have an interest in importing items from China that are covered by the additional duties. Accordingly, USTR will soon provide an opportunity for the public to request the exclusion of particular products from the additional duties subject to this action.  USTR will issue a notice in the Federal Register with details regarding this process within the next few weeks.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ustr.gov/about-us/policy-offices/press-office/press-releases/2018/june/ustr-issues-tariffs-chinese-products\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fustr.gov%2Fabout-us%2Fpolicy-offices%2Fpress-office%2Fpress-releases%2F2018%2Fjune%2Fustr-issues-tariffs-chinese-products&d=4I0nUGy1hPUuHKx6tC%2BvAKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=76a746a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ustr.gov/about-us/policy-offices/press-office/press-releases/2018/june/ustr-issues-tariffs-chinese-products</a><br />\n<br />\n6月15日份野一早有提過"},{"pid":"660fb52e5185fa34963d7aee8399fb9cab4b3cca","tid":733718,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"自己後知後覺就話人突然軟化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要睇突然變軟就北望神周<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f459fb58fa4186cafe8525093d7d89a6a679fa","tid":733718,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/l6LZjaz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fl6LZjaz.png&h=f91b38b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50e9c68edc88f2aca74db93659a53d1826625e13","tid":733718,"uid":51840,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報 步入 Fake News 之列"},{"pid":"70d14f6ce37585295e257a579c5cdafd25250a84","tid":733718,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T04:32:17.000Z","msg